  "detailed_description": "<strong>Welcome to Ritum Bitum</strong><br>Ritum Bitum is a 2-in-1 concept: it is a rhythm game and keyboard simulator. The speed, color and position of the letters are determined by your music. Enjoy music while learning keyboard techniques.<br><br><strong>Your music in OGG format</strong><br>Place your music at \".../Ritum Bitum/Ritum Bitum/Content\".<br>Click \"Refresh\" if you added music after starting the game.<br><br><strong>Two game modes:</strong><br>- \"keyboard\" - press the corresponding key to catch the letter.<br>- \"mouse + keyboard\" - collect letters with the mouse, and collect bright letters with the corresponding key pressed.<br><br><strong>Customize the keys</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470690/extras/753314ab9c8338af14163df2301c16ad.poster.avif?t=1620724032\" width=628 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470690/extras/753314ab9c8338af14163df2301c16ad.webm?t=1620724032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470690/extras/753314ab9c8338af14163df2301c16ad.mp4?t=1620724032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Alternative colors</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470690/extras/fd16ebcf884bf878670504a280472fd6.poster.avif?t=1620724032\" width=628 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470690/extras/fd16ebcf884bf878670504a280472fd6.webm?t=1620724032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470690/extras/fd16ebcf884bf878670504a280472fd6.mp4?t=1620724032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Welcome to Ritum Bitum</strong><br>Ritum Bitum is a 2-in-1 concept: it is a rhythm game and keyboard simulator. The speed, color and position of the letters are determined by your music. Enjoy music while learning keyboard techniques.<br><br><strong>Your music in OGG format</strong><br>Place your music at \".../Ritum Bitum/Ritum Bitum/Content\".<br>Click \"Refresh\" if you added music after starting the game.<br><br><strong>Two game modes:</strong><br>- \"keyboard\" - press the corresponding key to catch the letter.<br>- \"mouse + keyboard\" - collect letters with the mouse, and collect bright letters with the corresponding key pressed.<br><br><strong>Customize the keys</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470690/extras/753314ab9c8338af14163df2301c16ad.poster.avif?t=1620724032\" width=628 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470690/extras/753314ab9c8338af14163df2301c16ad.webm?t=1620724032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470690/extras/753314ab9c8338af14163df2301c16ad.mp4?t=1620724032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Alternative colors</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470690/extras/fd16ebcf884bf878670504a280472fd6.poster.avif?t=1620724032\" width=628 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470690/extras/fd16ebcf884bf878670504a280472fd6.webm?t=1620724032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470690/extras/fd16ebcf884bf878670504a280472fd6.mp4?t=1620724032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></